to make sure their experience managing their site is as awesome as the experience that the users of their site have.</p>\n<p>We also create our own products &#8211; some WordPress related, some internal, some just as fun projects. We want to make the interfaces for those sing as well. I think this is a terrific opportunity to work with a top-notch team that knows how to execute and won&#8217;t compromise on vision or UX/UI experience.</p>\n<p>Think you&#8217;re right right person for the job? Can&#8217;t wait to <a href=\"http://crowdfavorite.com/jobs/\">hear from you</a>.</p>\n<p>I&#8217;m also very proud to be advertising this position on the excellent <a href=\"http://www.randsinrepose.com/onejob-jobs.html\">Rands in Repose website</a> as part of his <a href=\"http://www.randsinrepose.com/archives/2012/08/12/one_job.html\">One Job</a> sponsorship. I&#8217;ve known Michael for a long time, and I&#8217;m thrilled to be in a position to be able to support his excellent work and present this opportunity to his audience.</p>\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:7:\"pubDate\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:31:\"Tue, 04 Sep 2012 19:35:06 +0000\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:32:\"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/\";a:1:{s:7:\"creator\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:4:\"Alex\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}}}i:42;a:6:{s:4:\"data\";s:13:\"\n\x09\n\x09\n\x09\n\x09\n\x09\n\x09\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";s:5:\"child\";a:2:{s:0:\"\";a:5:{s:5:\"title\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:39:\"Joseph: WordCamp SLC (Utah) 2012 Update\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"guid\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:31:\"https://josephscott.org/?p=6364\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"link\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:70:\"http://josephscott.org/archives/2012/09/wordcamp-slc-utah-2012-update/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:11:\"description\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:734:\"<p>Quick update on the upcoming <a href=\"http://2012.slc.wordcamp.org/\">WordCamp SLC 2012</a> on September 22nd:</p>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"http://2012.slc.wordcamp.org/schedule/\">schedule</a> for the day is now live</li>\n<li>early bird pricing has ended, but we still have <a href=\"http://2012.slc.wordcamp.org/registration/\">general admission tickets</a>, with the still reasonable cost of $20</li>\n<li><a href=\"http://2012.slc.wordcamp.org/2012/09/04/shirt-orders-go-in-tomorrow/\">t-shirt order is going in tomorrow</a> so if you want to be assured a of shirt in your size you&#8217;ll need to register before the end of the day on September 5th.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Look forward to seeing everyone again on the 22nd up at the UoU campus.</p>\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:7:\"pubDate\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:31:\"Tue, 04 Sep 2012 16:34:26 +0000\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:32:\"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/\";a:1:{s:7:\"creator\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:12:\"Joseph Scott\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}}}i:43;a:6:{s:4:\"data\";s:13:\"\n\x09\n\x09\n\x09\n\x09\n\x09\n\x09\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";s:5:\"child\";a:2:{s:0:\"\";a:5:{s:5:\"title\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:68:\"Weblog Tools Collection: How not to Desig